The paper deals with shape analysis using diffeomorphisms, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of statistical analysis and optimization also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Finally, the investigation of symmetries and their properties is a topic in both computer science and mathematics, making cs.SY a possible category as well.
